title: Advanced Charts Add-on for WPBakery 1.5.2 - WordPress Plugin
description: Visit us on: https://www.nulledforums.org Advanced Charts for WPBakery WordPress Plugin is an add-on for WPBakery Page Builder (formerly Visual Composer). It allows the use of all the chart types from Chart.js with advanced chart settings enabled.
